<div style="position:absolute;left:36.75px;top:88.04px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">本次事故所有相關損害</span><span class="cls_006">，</span><span class="cls_005">雙方和解並同意不行使民刑事訴訟上權利</span><span class="cls_006">：</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.75px;top:112.56px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">第一條</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:102.25px;top:112.56px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">和解金額</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:116.25px;top:137.11px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">1. </span><span class="cls_005">甲方應修復</span><span class="cls_007">TEST</span><span class="cls_005">車輛於本次事故受損處。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:116.25px;top:160.51px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">2. </span><span class="cls_005">車輛應送回原廠修車廠修復。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:116.25px;top:183.52px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">3. </span><span class="cls_005">修車廠由甲方指定。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:116.25px;top:206.54px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">4. </span><span class="cls_005">甲方應額外支付乙方新台幣</span><span class="cls_006"> 1 </span><span class="cls_005">元整。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.75px;top:231.06px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">第二條</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:102.25px;top:231.06px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">當事人與其手機號碼</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:116.25px;top:255.58px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">1. </span><span class="cls_005">甲方</span><span class="cls_006">：123456 </span><span class="cls_005">駕駛</span><span class="cls_006">；</span><span class="cls_005">手機號碼</span><span class="cls_006">： 0919050778</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:116.25px;top:278.63px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">2. </span><span class="cls_005">乙方</span><span class="cls_006">：</span><span class="cls_007">TEST </span><span class="cls_005">駕駛</span><span class="cls_006">；</span><span class="cls_005">手機號碼</span><span class="cls_006">： 0908707801</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.75px;top:303.52px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">第三條</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:102.25px;top:303.52px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">本次交通事故相關資訊</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:116.25px;top:328.08px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">1. </span><span class="cls_005">事故地點</span><span class="cls_006">：403</span><span class="cls_005">台中市西區復興路三段</span><span class="cls_006">53</span><span class="cls_005">巷</span><span class="cls_006">33-2</span><span class="cls_005">號</span><span class="cls_006"> </span><span class="cls_007">Test</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:116.25px;top:351.47px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">2. </span><span class="cls_005">事故時間</span><span class="cls_006">：2021 </span><span class="cls_005">年</span><span class="cls_006"> 03 </span><span class="cls_005">月</span><span class="cls_006"> 12 </span><span class="cls_005">日</span><span class="cls_006"> 18 </span><span class="cls_005">時</span><span class="cls_006"> 57 </span><span class="cls_005">分</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:116.25px;top:374.49px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">3. </span><span class="cls_005">事故照片</span><span class="cls_006">：</span><span class="cls_005">如附件</span></div>
