<div style="position:absolute;left:116.25px;top:423.52px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">1. </span><span class="cls_005">甲方按修車廠之要求支付修車費。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:116.25px;top:446.54px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">2. </span><span class="cls_005">第一條第</span><span class="cls_006"> 4 </span><span class="cls_005">項部分</span><span class="cls_006">:</span><span class="cls_005">轉帳付款</span><span class="cls_006">-</span><span class="cls_005">甲方應於收到乙方受款帳號之</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:132.25px;top:469.56px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">通知後</span><span class="cls_006">，</span><span class="cls_005">在兩個工作天內</span><span class="cls_006">，</span><span class="cls_005">轉帳新台幣</span><span class="cls_006"> 1 </span><span class="cls_005">元予乙方。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.75px;top:494.07px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">第五條</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:102.25px;top:494.07px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">其他</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:116.25px;top:518.59px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">1. </span><span class="cls_005">雙方皆成年且同意將和解意願紀錄於此和解書。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:116.25px;top:541.61px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">2. </span><span class="cls_005">除已載條件外</span><span class="cls_006">，</span><span class="cls_005">甲乙雙方同意各自負責自己所駕駛車輛之損</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:132.25px;top:564.63px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">害與自己乘客之損傷。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.00px;top:621.89px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">雙方表達和解意願之方式如後</span></div>
